{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/tv/2020/05/28/降魔的，建国后鬼神都去香港了.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"8e57d337-c294-5f97-bcf3-2907eb72d0f8","excerpt":"降魔的，建国后鬼神都去香港了 去年看过「金宵大厦」后，我就开始关注 TVB 的鬼神片了，最近听说「降魔的 2.0」上映，看了一集没看懂，于是把 2017 年的第一季也看了。这篇文章写在看完 2.0 的第 1…","html":"<h1>降魔的，建国后鬼神都去香港了</h1>\n<p>去年看过「金宵大厦」后，我就开始关注 TVB 的鬼神片了，最近听说「降魔的 2.0」上映，看了一集没看懂，于是把 2017 年的第一季也看了。这篇文章写在看完 2.0 的第 18 集之后。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/759f74ea470cabd0faae7d292e78a4ae/08d92/2020-05-28-stone.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/759f74ea470cabd0faae7d292e78a4ae/cbe2e/2020-05-28-stone.webp 148w,\n/static/759f74ea470cabd0faae7d292e78a4ae/3084c/2020-05-28-stone.webp 295w,\n/static/759f74ea470cabd0faae7d292e78a4ae/5ca24/2020-05-28-stone.webp 590w,\n/static/759f74ea470cabd0faae7d292e78a4ae/dad35/2020-05-28-stone.webp 885w,\n/static/759f74ea470cabd0faae7d292e78a4ae/2baf0/2020-05-28-stone.webp 1180w,\n/static/759f74ea470cabd0faae7d292e78a4ae/74c35/2020-05-28-stone.webp 1521w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/759f74ea470cabd0faae7d292e78a4ae/a80bd/2020-05-28-stone.jpg 148w,\n/static/759f74ea470cabd0faae7d292e78a4ae/1c91a/2020-05-28-stone.jpg 295w,\n/static/759f74ea470cabd0faae7d292e78a4ae/1c72d/2020-05-28-stone.jpg 590w,\n/static/759f74ea470cabd0faae7d292e78a4ae/a8a14/2020-05-28-stone.jpg 885w,\n/static/759f74ea470cabd0faae7d292e78a4ae/fbd2c/2020-05-28-stone.jpg 1180w,\n/static/759f74ea470cabd0faae7d292e78a4ae/08d92/2020-05-28-stone.jpg 1521w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/759f74ea470cabd0faae7d292e78a4ae/1c72d/2020-05-28-stone.jpg\"\n          alt=\"石敢当\"\n          title=\"石敢当\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">石敢当</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>「降魔的」主要讲出租司机马季一泡尿解封被封印百年的石精灵「石敢当」，石敢当为报答解封之恩，答应帮马季养母找亲生儿子豪仔的灵魂，不料，在为马季开天眼时能力被马季吸收，马季因此成为降魔人。为了灭掉一个魔，石敢当把自己的全部能量给马季，并和魔同归于尽。第一季结尾，马季终于碰到豪仔的灵魂。</p>\n<p>第二季目前讲的是豪仔和海魔做过交易，必须吃人续命，于是找到马季希望能帮忙消灭海魔以解开诅咒。</p>\n<p>比较喜欢这部剧环境的设定，比如鬼是人死后为了完成遗愿存在，完成愿望就会去所谓的「目的地」，精灵则是因为被人赋予情感而成形，比如「莉莉」是一个洋娃娃幻化的精灵、「风狮爷」是一个寄予一个爱情故事的石像，魔的存在就更有趣，第一季的大 boss，黑鼠尾草是吸收很多人的血幻化而成，第二季的谎言魔是一幅多年被倒卖的假画幻化而成。</p>\n<p>第二季又引入科学解释，搞得这部剧多了些反迷信的色彩（虽然它是鬼片），更加感兴趣它后面的发展了。</p>","frontmatter":{"category":"tv"},"fields":{"slug":"/tv/2020/05/28/降魔的，建国后鬼神都去香港了.html","date":"May 28, 2020","title":"降魔的，建国后鬼神都去香港了"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/tv/2020/05/28/降魔的，建国后鬼神都去香港了.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/life/2020/05/20/记录下京东购买乐行天下被骗经历.html","title":"记录下京东购买乐行天下被骗经历"},"frontmatter":{"category":"life"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/fe/2020/05/29/WebRTC，谈谈我这几天对它的研究.html","title":"WebRTC，谈谈我这几天对它的研究"},"frontmatter":{"category":"fe"}}}}}